<h3 id="<%= country.abbr %>" href="/<%= country.name %>" class="country-legal">
          <img class="sitemap-link-flag" src=<%=image_url("country-flags/#{country.abbr.downcase}.svg")%> alt=<%="#{country.name} Flag"%>>
          <span class="country-title"><%= country.name.titleize.gsub("-", " ") %></span>
          <div class=legality-status><%= show_svg('green-check.svg')%> Legal</div>
          </h3>
<div class="legal-description">
  <p>Bitcoin and other cryptocurrencies are legal to trade and hold in Bosnia and Herzegovina.</p>
  <p>The Central Bank of Bosnia and Herzegovina <a href="https://vijesti.ba/clanak/389130/o-kriptovalutama-se-potrebno-detaljno-informirati-ulozeni-novac-nije-osiguran" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">announced</a> that there were no plans to limit or prevent transacting in virtual currencies.</p>
</div>